{"tid":2373903,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"咪又離棄 撐未永恆 侵粉無義氣 (不喜勿插）","createTime":"2021-01-20T22:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T23:14:41.000Z","uid":371912,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4a42d1e7cf0ba77a9c78994589918a9574713d","tid":2373903,"uid":371912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T22:54:02.000Z","msg":"有侵侵冇登　還是望佢更 <br />\n強硬與多國合盟　對抗不能等<br />\n<br />\n對侵侵不息的愛　佢未可替代<br />\n這侵侵　和習帝　有幾招　全奉送<br />\n<br />\n童戀的拜登　無論痕又痕<br />\n還是靠誤導內容　令拜登成功<br />\n<br />\n侵侵會　永遠都存在　共你同在　無盡永恆中<br />\n<br />\n有著你　便撐著佢　侵粉是永不死<br />\n到拜登贏左　竟扮支持他<br />\n<br />\n冇著你　就撐著佢　講到又撐到死<br />\n咪又離棄　撐未永恆 侵粉無義氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3024dce7fadd4a9ff19c9c5ccb8df304ffe96687","tid":2373903,"uid":222938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T23:14:41.000Z","msg":"知道係愛是永恆但好多句唔啱音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}